description.en:
Whether you are new to crypto or an enthusiast, using Xion.Finance is an easy way to start earning a passive income and spending your Xion Global Token(XGT) rewards on everyday products. 

It is a cross-chain yield farming protocol on ETH, xDAI, BSC chain. Benefiting XGT owners with low-cost swaps, attractive liquidity mining, lending, NFTs & purchasing power to shop online.

With various cross-chain mechanisms and bridges built, users can easily swap XGT, BNB, ETH and xDAI seamlessly between chains for low-cost liquidity provision, payments and rewards.

To get started you'll first need to acquire BNB and/or xDAI on Xion Finance in order to provide liquidity to these trading pairs: XGT-BNB, XGT-xDAI. In return, you'll get up to 200% APY, trading fees, rare NFTs and purchasing power to shop online with XGT.

This protocol has been audited by CertiK and is trading on PancakeSwap, Honeyswap and Uniswap.

Learn more by checking out our GitBook on Xion Finance
